  "description": "<b>微软日前发布的&#160;Xbox&#160;One&#160;遭到阵阵骂声，与此同时，索尼&#160;PS4&#160;则笼络了更多用户的心。对于不断扑面而来的批评声，微软欧洲市场高管&#160;Chris&#160;Lewis&#160;认为这很不公平，回应称该等&#160;Xbox&#160;One&#160;上市后由消费者来评价。</b>Chris&#160;Lewis&#160;说，我觉得这很不公平，因为我觉得它应该等今年年底上市后再由我们的用户来评价。我们现在所处的位置是改革游戏和娱乐的方式，我们处在一个前所未有的位置。它将由也应该由消费者通过&#160;Xbox&#160;One&#160;体验游戏和娱乐之后再做出反馈。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d6b22f3/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241460.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%BA%94%E7%AD%89Xbox+One%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82%E5%90%8E%E5%86%8D%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241460.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%BA%94%E7%AD%89Xbox+One%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82%E5%90%8E%E5%86%8D%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241460.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%BA%94%E7%AD%89Xbox+One%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82%E5%90%8E%E5%86%8D%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241460.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%BA%94%E7%AD%89Xbox+One%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82%E5%90%8E%E5%86%8D%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241460.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%BA%94%E7%AD%89